erished in the forest, their spirit possessed a tree stump, causing the spirit\u2019s rebirth as this Pok\u00e9mon."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "An unknown spirit came to lodge in a tree stump, creating this Pok\u00e9mon. A cure-all can be made from an infusion of its green leaves."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "By imitating the voice of a child, it causes people to get hopelessly lost deep in the forest. It\u2019s trying to make friends with them."}, {"version": "x", "text": "These Pok\u00e9mon are created when spirits possess rotten tree stumps. They prefer to live in abandoned forests."}, {"version": "y", "text": "According to old tales, these Pok\u00e9mon are stumps possessed by the spirits of children who died while lost in the forest."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "moon", "omega-ruby", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "phantump"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "trevenant"}]}